msgid ""
"The ``LOCALCONFDIR`` points to the directory that contains configuration "
"files (``/usr/local/etc/couchdb`` by default). This variable may vary from "
"the target operation system and may be changed during building from the "
"source code. For binary distributions, it mostly points to the installation "
"path (e.g. ``C:\\Program Files\\CouchDB\\etc\\couchdb`` for Windows)."
